## Naming Conventions

| Entity | Convention | Example |
|--------|-----------|---------|
| Files and folders | `kebab-case` | `auth-middleware.rs`, `api-design/` |
| Rust functions and variables | `snake_case` | `parse_request`, `user_id` |
| Rust types and traits | `PascalCase` | `AuthService`, `Encryptable` |
| Rust constants | `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE` | `MAX_RETRIES`, `DEFAULT_TIMEOUT` |
| Rust modules | `snake_case` | `mod crypto_utils` |
| Workflow folders | `NN-kebab-description` | `01-new-module`, `05-code-review` |
| ADR files | `ADR-NNNN-kebab-title.md` | `ADR-0001-use-axum.md` |

