## Skills, Commands, and Plugins Rules

1. **Check this file first** — before generating any new skill, command, or plugin,
   verify one does not already exist here or in `syntek-rust-security`.

2. **Propose before generating** — if a new skill/command/plugin is needed, propose it
   to the user before generating it.

3. **Register on approval** — once approved, add it to this file under the relevant section.

4. **Distinguish ephemeral vs. promoted** — single-use commands are ephemeral and not
   registered here. Reusable, reviewed skills are promoted and registered.

### Available commands (via syntek-rust-security plugin)

Security: `/vuln-scan`, `/crypto-review`, `/memory-audit`, `/threat-model`, `/scan-secrets`,
`/supply-chain-audit`, `/binary-check`, `/compliance-report`, `/pentest-tools`, `/fuzz-setup`

Cryptography: `/encrypt-setup`, `/decrypt-setup`, `/zeroize-audit`, `/minimize-unsafe`, `/ffi-audit`

Infrastructure: `/vault-setup`, `/token-rotate`, `/ssh-wrapper`, `/cert-rotate`,
`/cloudflare-setup`, `/docker-harden`, `/backup-setup`, `/firewall-setup`, `/server-harden`

AI Gateway: `/ai-gateway-setup`, `/ai-provider-add`

Server Stack: `/nginx-config`, `/gunicorn-config`, `/redis-config`, `/systemd-harden`

Code Quality: `/review-code`, `/refactor-code`, `/design-api`, `/write-tests`,
`/benchmark`, `/generate-docs`, `/version-bump`, `/git-workflow`, `/manage-deps`

