## Gap Registration Rule

If Claude encounters a workflow folder that contains only `CONTEXT.md` and is missing
`STEPS.md` or `CHECKLIST.md`, Claude MUST:

1. Log the gap in `/GAPS.md` at the project root with the missing file path and a
   suggested one-line description of what the file should contain
2. Proceed using `CONTEXT.md` alone as best-effort guidance
3. Never generate and silently commit missing workflow files without explicit user instruction

To fill a gap: `/scaffold --fill-gaps <workflow-path>`

